  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death City is a story about the protagonist, Roy, who repeatedly faces death in a zombie apocalypse world and strives to overcome his fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/05dfac1a4ef85c437429e1106971b146.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/05dfac1a4ef85c437429e1106971b146.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/716974e12db5338511feb1f5488bddc5.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/716974e12db5338511feb1f5488bddc5.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The early gameplay requires players to progress the story while avoiding dangerous entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/01d9075afe2d2938b87377063f23cb37.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/01d9075afe2d2938b87377063f23cb37.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will experience various story events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/f5bf7c045bd63f1655547723f651cd14.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/f5bf7c045bd63f1655547723f651cd14.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=460 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once firearms are obtained, players can attack enemies, with a total of three different firearms available during gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/c8ad7bb954a4812bfe1c873bef626d60.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/c8ad7bb954a4812bfe1c873bef626d60.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to shooting actions, there are various types of puzzles throughout the gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/d39d51930d3464deaa30bd48e064f11f.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/d39d51930d3464deaa30bd48e064f11f.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can make different choices during the game, which will affect the ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/d5bd2c7f49a4576e2f3c4ce7e453a3f6.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/d5bd2c7f49a4576e2f3c4ce7e453a3f6.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/191d5fccf51cdefb41d61500565eecde.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/191d5fccf51cdefb41d61500565eecde.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features choices that determine Roy's destiny, with multiple endings based on the truths uncovered and the decisions made along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/c4a533daf07778d05eb653cc89111ac7.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/c4a533daf07778d05eb653cc89111ac7.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death City is a story about the protagonist, Roy, who repeatedly faces death in a zombie apocalypse world and strives to overcome his fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/05dfac1a4ef85c437429e1106971b146.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/05dfac1a4ef85c437429e1106971b146.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/716974e12db5338511feb1f5488bddc5.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/716974e12db5338511feb1f5488bddc5.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The early gameplay requires players to progress the story while avoiding dangerous entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/01d9075afe2d2938b87377063f23cb37.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/01d9075afe2d2938b87377063f23cb37.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will experience various story events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/f5bf7c045bd63f1655547723f651cd14.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/f5bf7c045bd63f1655547723f651cd14.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=460 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once firearms are obtained, players can attack enemies, with a total of three different firearms available during gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/c8ad7bb954a4812bfe1c873bef626d60.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/c8ad7bb954a4812bfe1c873bef626d60.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to shooting actions, there are various types of puzzles throughout the gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/d39d51930d3464deaa30bd48e064f11f.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/d39d51930d3464deaa30bd48e064f11f.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can make different choices during the game, which will affect the ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/d5bd2c7f49a4576e2f3c4ce7e453a3f6.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/d5bd2c7f49a4576e2f3c4ce7e453a3f6.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/191d5fccf51cdefb41d61500565eecde.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/191d5fccf51cdefb41d61500565eecde.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features choices that determine Roy's destiny, with multiple endings based on the truths uncovered and the decisions made along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras/c4a533daf07778d05eb653cc89111ac7.avif?t=1731485613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265000/extras_big/c4a533daf07778d05eb653cc89111ac7.avif?t=1731485613 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
